Levels all done, in the file place, everyone try try i'm sure they'll 
work.

Two things to watch out for..

One: The slime levels (you'll know them when you see them) kinda 
crank your levels, but only if you've done the right thing and gone 
through all the normal levels already. otherwise, you'll probably 
die :D

Two: The mage levels (they're pretty easy to spot too) sometimes 
crashed the game on my laptop, however, the game regularly crashes on 
my laptop (it's old) i'm pretty sure they'll work fine on newer 
computers. if not, no biggie, just restart the game. the second time 
always proved to be the charm.

any errors you find can be emailed to me at the shiny blue link next 
to this message, grammatical, difficulty wise, ridiculous, i dunno

til next time:
